        "text": "the Asherim",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". From such passages as this we may conclude that the images of Asherah were generally of wood.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
